Release Notes
Based on Trend Reversal Alert Hybrid [TRAH] indicator which is a hybrid script of simple reversal strategy trading and Fibonacci levels. This version has the same fine-tuning as Trend-Reversal-Alerts-Strategy-Advanced but provides higher profit. Version update from 2nd to 6th.
